reviewText:
Movie was ok, but not my cup of tea. Too many monsters for my taste, however the comedy aspect is very funny. It can go to the grotesque quickly, but there is not too many gross parts.
It is a decent movie, better than some, but not as good as others. If you are into watching monsters and demons, then this would be up your alley.
